&lt;p&gt;ZSE40A is a digital vacuum sensor with a 4 digit, 2 color display.&#xa0; Instantaneous readings are shown in red or green, or shifted from one to the other to alert reaching a target condition.&#xa0; Switch outputs are also indicated on the display.&#xa0; Additional functions enhance security, power saving, resolution and stability.&#xa0; Reduce effort and input errors by copying settings to up to 10 sensors.&#xa0; Includes M8 cable connector.&#xa0; ZSE40A is UL/CSA, CE and RoHS compliant,with an IP65 enclosure rating.&lt;/p&gt;
